title: Russia kills IS-linked militant in Dagestan
text:
Russia: kills IS-linked militant in Dagestan 
The Hindu Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Russian security forces killed a militant linked to Islamic State in the North Caucasus republic of Dagestan early on Saturday, the government's Anti-Terrorist Committee (NAK) said, according to news agencies....
